Pharmstandard Climbs for 3rd Day as First-Half Profit Rises

-- B y   J a s o n   C o r c o r a n
-- 
2011-08-31T15:12:14Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-31/pharmstandard-climbs-for-3rd-day-as-first-half-profit-rises-52-.html
OAO  Pharmstandard (PHST)  rallied for a
third day after the Russian drugmaker said first-half profit
gained 52 percent on the year to 4.19 billion rubles ($145
million).  The shares rose as much as 6 percent before closing 0.7
percent higher at 2,090 rubles as of 6:45 p.m. in Moscow.  To contact the reporter on this story:
